Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Collective bargaining law
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b0407bx6
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 27 Feb 1977
Labour and Carter row over change to collective bargaining legislation. Are US TV viewers seeing too much news? The sound quality on this recording is variable/poor. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less